reviewText: My granddaughter enjoys it during playtime. I love the AUTO PLAY. Thank you
My grand daughter loves Barney! Can't wait to give this her for Christmas.

My kids love Barney, this pink dinosaur will never get old.
Just wonderful.

My 17 month old daughter is a HUGE Barney fan!  We watch his show every day on PBS.  We have 2 other Barney DVD's besides this one -- and this is her favorite one by a mile.  It is "new Barney" as stated by another reviewer -- and we love that!  I think she loves it so much because she recognizes the children from the daily PBS show.  This DVD is packed with catchy songs about healthy eating and exercising -- who can argue with that?

I just bought this at Target and I can't even watch it.  My almost 2 year old LOVES his other Barney tape, so I thought this would be a good one....WRONG.  This is the "new" Barney and, if you ask me, it stinks!  My kid lost interest in 5 minutes which NEVER happens with his other tape that he's watched probably a hundred times!!
